		<path d="M8 1C4.14 1 1 4.14 1 8s3.14 7 7 7 7-3.14 7-7-3.14-7-7-7zm2.5 5.5a1 1 0 1 1 0 2 1 1 0 0 1 0-2zm-5 0a1 1 0 1 1 0 2 1 1 0 0 1 0-2zm6 3.5c-.55.83-1.4 1.5-3.5 1.5S5.05 10.83 4.5 10h7z" />
	</svg>
